    Welcome to base PHP image with Nginx!

    Installed:
    - composer
    - composer plugin for faster downloads: hirak/prestissimo
    - xdebug (global script *php-enable-xdebug* and *php-disable-xdebug* available); disabled by default
    - opcache (php-enable-opcache and php-disable-opcache); disabled by default

    Have a nice day :)!

    P.S. You can cat private key for access this container through SSH:
    cat /root/.ssh/id_rsa
